body: # SJE Rhombus This page contains links to download the AutomateIt program suite as well as documentation on how to use it. ### AutomateIt Applications for SJE Rhombus Click here to download the latest version of the AutomateIt program suite. ### Documentation Check back shortly, documentation will be added soon! ### Support or Contact The AutomateIt software suite was written and is maintained by Kanyon Edvall (@kedvall) For help or bug reports please send an email to kedvall123@gmail.com with the subject line **SJE Support**
